{"tid":1240406,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"NOW新聞：憤怒政治難持續　皆因怒火無轉化行動","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:27:25.000Z","uid":27045,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2df3fed262e518a463da6bd4d33be687e570a54e","tid":1240406,"uid":27045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】過去七個月，法國每逢周末都有黃背心示威活動，最高峰時有30萬人參加，但在最新一輪的示威人數只有數以千計，聲勢已大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n2011年爆發的佔領華爾街曾「遍地開花」，由紐約蔓延至美國其他城市，甚至世界各地，但隨着民眾的熱情退卻，參加者的人數逐漸減少，活動亦隨之結束。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟學人》雜誌曾指，21世紀是憤怒政治的世紀，兩個大規模示威活動均後勁不繼，或要歸咎於示威者無將公眾的怒火，轉化成實質的政治行動。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心運動是法國自二戰以來最長時間的一次示威活動，由反對政府調高燃油稅而起，在民眾的怒吼聲下政府屈服，但運動之後失去焦點，即使示威持續，有示威者說氣氛已經大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n美國老牌政論雜誌《新共和》就形容運動已經沒有了最基本的政治前提，「怒氣」似乎已所餘無幾，示威者亦無更好地利用更多刺激因素，推動停滯不前的示威活運動。<br />\n<br />\n《新共和》指，示威者不但杯葛總統馬克龍讓民眾暢所欲言的全國大辯論，在運動初期亦無就燃料稅問題要求任何立法，一度聯手的極左和極右兩派又再現分歧。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱代表黃背心運動的黨派最後在上月的歐洲議會選舉中，得票率不足百分之一，無法在歐洲議會佔一席位。<br />\n<br />\n情況就好像佔領華爾街一樣，示威者抗議巨企貪婪不公，影響美國政治，還有社會不平等，當時示威者有絕佳的條件，金融危機加上屬民主黨的總統在位，但示威者沒有有效利用，沒有跟政策制訂者建立關係，亦沒有提出任何改變相關政策的建議。<br />\n<br />\n結果無論是佔領華爾街，還是黃背心示威運動，都跟過去十年的「憤怒政治」所面對的困境一樣，因為「怒氣」不足，而逐漸失去活力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=352224&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352224%26refer%3D&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvws5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=396a8c5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352224%26refer%3D&h=e8139c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=352224&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"7a0ae9cdb8822c00d2822d2561a3ab02635a8ceb","tid":1240406,"uid":27045,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭：贏硬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4GoWsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4GoWsL.png&h=1191b24f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"492f04d4804045e08b72320b7a5ad115027e9ed3","tid":1240406,"uid":131259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\n熱情會冷卻，應趁現勢盡快進行實際的政治行動"},{"pid":"a3191c2a48784bc81299a92dbcd697e788418934","tid":1240406,"uid":27045,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"492f04d4804045e08b72320b7a5ad115027e9ed3","tid":1240406,"uid":131259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\n熱情會冷卻，應趁現勢盡快進行實際的政治行動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"616之後已經見唔少港豬回復食玩瞓mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d327d37e87fd1525789fa76d40b6d18d3a2cb301","tid":1240406,"uid":27045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">怒火丶行動 都唔可以停</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa4cf3f31c5339d0c87e193ea55ef1c6debafec","tid":1240406,"uid":65601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"實際政治行動姐係咩？"},{"pid":"e70066a8e6e90a258b150119efd9cd7f641e90c5","tid":1240406,"uid":27045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa4cf3f31c5339d0c87e193ea55ef1c6debafec","tid":1240406,"uid":65601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T